{"tid":198733,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[美劇] 召喚所有鐘意Grey's Anatomy既人","createTime":"2017-04-12T17:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T18:59:10.000Z","uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"606ad87e36c090b7a3c768c2c98b6f4167c2845b","tid":198733,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"見成日有人傾美劇 但都好少會提到Grey's Anatomy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲同我一樣都好鐘意呢套劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;The medical drama series focuses on a group of doctors at a hospital in Seattle, including several who began their careers at the facility as interns. One of the doctors and the show's namesake, Meredith Grey, is the daughter of a famous surgeon. She struggles to maintain relationships with her colleagues, particularly the hospital's one-time chief of surgery, Richard Webber, due to a pre-existing relationship between them -- Webber and Meredith's mother had a personal relationship when Meredith was young.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/13/010144_e1877e686574fac922904b3c1f37aa56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F010144_e1877e686574fac922904b3c1f37aa56.jpg&h=fa8665aa&s={SIZE}\" />最鐘意係呢個時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d3bac489772411a98754f7df18b97707dcc066","tid":198733,"uid":18786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見成日有人傾美劇 但都好少會提到Grey's Anatomy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲同我一樣都好鐘意呢套劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;The medical drama series focuses on a group of doctors at a hospital in Seattle, including several who began their careers at the facility as interns. One of the doctors and the show's namesake, Meredith Grey, is the daughter of a famous surgeon. She struggles to maintain relationships with her colleagues, particularly the hospital's one-time chief of surgery, Richard Webber, due to a pre-existing relationship between them -- Webber and Meredith's mother had a personal relationship when Meredith was young.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/13/010144_e1877e686574fac922904b3c1f37aa56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F010144_e1877e686574fac922904b3c1f37aa56.jpg&h=fa8665aa&s={SIZE}\" />最鐘意係呢個時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上星期開始追 而家先追到第三季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac61a1ab2aa3f0bee42e0edf0bbb7886dfc92c2","tid":198733,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上星期開始追 而家先追到第三季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇話最鐘意邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到後期會好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011ea43950ac44d4f45588355aa32179b3f81a07","tid":198733,"uid":30764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T19:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟美國進度<br />\n<br />\nOwen同Amelia快d離婚啦，拖咗好耐，好煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nApril今季又係好bitchy<br />\n大媽麻煩俾番d劇情Alex<img src=\"/assets/faces/n